msgid ""
msgstr ""
"Project-Id-Version: Yakuza 6 Translation\n"
"Last-Translator: SavT\n"
"MIME-Version: 1.0\n"
"Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8\n"
"Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit\n"
"Language: it\n"

msgctxt "0||||4"
msgid "So the victims were one man and one woman.\r\nYou didn't know either of them, right Kiryu?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1||||4"
msgid "Right. I only ever saw a photo of Tatsukawa,\r\nand I definitely don't recognize the woman."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2||||4"
msgid "I see. I guess that's that, then."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3||||4"
msgid "But weren't you saying that this Tatsukawa\r\nfellow is the father of that baby?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4||||4"
msgid "In other words, he's a sleazy ex-host who\r\nknocked up a girl you treat as a daughter."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5||||4"
msgid "It wouldn't be such a far-fetched story\r\nfor you to kill a man for that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||||4"
msgid "Easy, Honjo.\r\nHe's not our suspect here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7||||4"
msgid "Until we can prove otherwise,\r\neveryone involved is a suspect."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8||||4"
msgid "After Tatsukawa left his job as a host,\r\nhe spent a lot of time in Little Asia."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9||||4"
msgid "Apparently he was working as\r\nan informant for the triads."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10||||4"
msgid "Were the police aware of that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11||||4"
msgid "No, he wasn't even on our radar."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12||||4"
msgid "But I think it's pretty clear-cut who\r\nkilled Tatsukawa... The Saio Triad."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13||||4"
msgid "The murder weapon and modus operandi\r\nline up with some other Saio incidents."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||||4"
msgid "By the way, the female victim who was with\r\nTatsukawa was a Kamurocho-based hostess."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "15||||4"
msgid "Dating him unfortunately landed her\r\nin the wrong place at the wrong time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "16||||4"
msgid "Date-san. You shouldn't be divulging\r\nso many details about an open case."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||||4"
msgid "Kiryu went all the way to Hiroshima\r\nto find the father of that child."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "18||||4"
msgid "Then for the father to turn up dead here,\r\nhe probably knows more than we do."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||||4"
msgid "It's also thanks to Kiryu that we ID'd\r\nTatsukawa so quickly."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "20||||4"
msgid "I figure, it's only fair to be upfront\r\nabout the intel we've got."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "21||||4"
msgid "From where I'm standing, it looks\r\nmore like collusion. How about that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "22||||4"
msgid "He's been out of the yakuza for years, man."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "23||||4"
msgid "It's okay, Date-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||||4"
msgid "By the way, can you drop by Serena later?\r\nI still have some questions for you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||||4"
msgid "That sounds good. I'll come alone.\r\nYou go on over and wait for me, Kiryu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "26||||4"
msgid "Right. See you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "27||||4"
msgid "(Nagumo and Yuta are waiting at Serena.\r\nI should head there myself...)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-aniki."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||||4"
msgid "How'd it go?\r\nY'get anythin' from the cops?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "31||||4"
msgid "A few details, yeah."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "32||||4"
msgid "By the way, a detective friend of mine named\r\nDate is going to be stopping by here later."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33||||4"
msgid "He's married to the mama here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||||4"
msgid "Sorry about this, Mama.\r\nWe're always using your place for meetings."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||||4"
msgid "I don't mind, you can use it however you want.\r\nYou go back further with this place than I do."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||||4"
msgid "Thanks."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "37||||4"
msgid "So that Mama...\r\nShe's hitched to a detective?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "38||||4"
msgid "Good thing I didn't go puttin' my moves\r\non 'er. Ain't that right, Yuta?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||||4"
msgid "Are you all right, Yuta?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||||4"
msgid "'Parently this is the first time he's\r\nseen someone he knows dead."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||||4"
msgid "It's got 'im really down in the dumps."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||||4"
msgid "He wasn't askin' you. Besides Cap, you've\r\nbeen just as quiet as me until right now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||||4"
msgid "Listen, y'ass. I was jus' stayin'\r\nquiet t'give ya yer space."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||||4"
msgid "According to the police, the triads\r\nwere the ones who killed Tatsukawa."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||||4"
msgid "You're talkin' about the Saio Triad, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||||4"
msgid "Yeah. If you remember, Tatsukawa was\r\nworking as an informant for them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "49||||4"
msgid "It's possible he made a mistake\r\nand paid the price for it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||||4"
msgid "Those guys did some\r\nreal messed up shit, man."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "51||||4"
msgid "First they slit his throat, then stabbed 'im.\r\nWere they tryin' t'make an example?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||||4"
msgid "Somehow, it's like that dead guy\r\nback there wasn't the Tatsukawa I knew."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||||4"
msgid "I thought he came\r\nt'Kamurocho to be a host."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "54||||4"
msgid "But then it turns out he was\r\na triad informant."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||||4"
msgid "And just when we pin him down,\r\nhe winds up dead as a rat."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||||4"
msgid "Y'know, I came to Tokyo so I could beat\r\nTatsukawa to death for what he did..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||||4"
msgid "...But now I don't know what to think."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||||4"
msgid "So what's the plan, Aniki?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "59||||4"
msgid "Tatsukawa's literally a dead end,\r\nand anything about Haruka-san died with 'im."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||||4"
msgid "I know that. But I need to figure out\r\nwhy he was killed by the Chinese."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||||4"
msgid "Why's that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||||4"
msgid "If Tatsukawa had the triads coming after him,\r\nHaruka and Haruto might be involved, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||||4"
msgid "If that's true, does that mean Haruka's\r\naccident wasn't an accident at all?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||||4"
msgid "I don't know enough to say for sure."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||||4"
msgid "Either way, we have a lot to learn\r\nabout Tatsukawa's life here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "67||||4"
msgid "Yeah, you're right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||||4"
msgid "Kiryu. Mind if I join you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "69||||4"
msgid "So you're Hiroshima's Hirose Family?\r\nAnd you're involved with the Yomei Alliance?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "70||||4"
msgid "Yeah we're Yomei, but we report t'the\r\nMasuzoe Family. We're the bottom rung."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||||4"
msgid "But back in the day, our patriarch Toru Hirose\r\nused t'really whoop on the Omi Alliance."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||||4"
msgid "A cop like you'd know his name, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "73||||4"
msgid "Can't say that I do."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||||4"
msgid "Y'serious? Guess Tokyo detectives ain't\r\nthe hotshots they pretend t'be."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "75||||4"
msgid "Anyway, Kiryu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "76||||4"
msgid "I have something I need to tell\r\nyou about Haruka's situation."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "77||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "78||||4"
msgid "While you were down in Hiroshima,\r\nI moved her out of her room at Touto."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "79||||4"
msgid "She's at the police hospital now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80||||4"
msgid "Something happen?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||||4"
msgid "Yeah, we started getting frequent calls\r\nfrom people who claimed to be Tojo men."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "82||||4"
msgid "They insisted they wanted to see Haruka,\r\nand wouldn't stop calling us about her."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "83||||4"
msgid "The Tojo Clan wanted Haruka?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||||4"
msgid "Well, there's no way to verify if they\r\nwere really Tojo Clan guys or not."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||||4"
msgid "Better safe than sorry, though.\r\nThat's why I had her transferred over."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "86||||4"
msgid "And just in case, I have her room under\r\nsupervision so nobody gets too close."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "87||||4"
msgid "Has her condition improved at all?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "88||||4"
msgid "Unfortunately, no."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "89||||4"
msgid "If I can offer my opinion here, I'd say\r\nyou should avoid her until things calm down."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "90||||4"
msgid "If someone tailed you and learned where she\r\nwas, I'd be all out of places to keep her."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "91||||4"
msgid "I see..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "92||||4"
msgid "I just wish she'd wake up already..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||||4"
msgid "What's Akiyama up to?\r\nHe was watching Haruka, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||||4"
msgid "I asked him to keep his distance after\r\nwe transferred her to the police hospital."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||||4"
msgid "Remember, the triads are gunning for him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "96||||4"
msgid "It would be a disaster if they found\r\nhim hanging around our hospital."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "97||||4"
msgid "Can you contact him?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "98||||4"
msgid "I have some questions I'd like\r\nto ask him regarding the Chinese."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||||4"
msgid "Nope. He said he'd give me a call\r\nif he ever needs something."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "100||||4"
msgid "He didn't leave me any contact info."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||||4"
msgid "Either way, how is talking to\r\nAkiyama going to help you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "102||||4"
msgid "When we were together earlier, we fought\r\nagainst a large Chinese man named Ed."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||||4"
msgid "I'd bet he's a Saio officer."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104||||4"
msgid "If anyone can tell me where that\r\nguy might be, it's Akiyama."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||||4"
msgid "And once I find Ed, I want to ask him\r\nwhy the Saio killed Tatsukawa."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "106||||4"
msgid "I understand. But you know that's\r\nlaw enforcement's job, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "107||||4"
msgid "Well, not like that's ever stopped you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "109||||4"
msgid "Regardless, I need some answers, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "110||||4"
msgid "How Tatsukawa ended up in Kamurocho,\r\nhis disposition, his interactions with Haruka."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "111||||4"
msgid "Anything helps."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "112||||4"
msgid "Sorry, just doing my job."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "113||||4"
msgid "That Date fella ain't half bad.\r\nHe's still real sharp fer an old fart."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "114||||4"
msgid "Seems real trustworthy, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||||4"
msgid "Right. Maybe we should leave\r\nall o' this to Date-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "116||||4"
msgid "He might be able to find out\r\nwhy Tatsukawa had to die like that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "117||||4"
msgid "I'm sure he could, but I need to know now.\r\nThe earlier we learn the truth, the better."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "118||||4"
msgid "I'm not going to just sit around\r\nhere and wait for things to happen."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "119||||4"
msgid "Why're you in such a hurry?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "120||||4"
msgid "With the police on the Tatsukawa case,\r\nour trail is going to get cut off soon."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "121||||4"
msgid "Outside of Date-san, the force doesn't\r\ntake half measures here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "122||||4"
msgid "Earlier today, a detective named Honjo\r\nwas already treating me like a suspect."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "123||||4"
msgid "Wh-What the hell!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||||4"
msgid "I need to take care of this before it's too late."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "125||||4"
msgid "I'm going to start by looking for Akiyama.\r\nI'll start with his sewer hideout from before."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||||4"
msgid "You should stay here in the meantime.\r\nJust make sure I can reach you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "127||||4"
msgid "We'll keep an eye out while yer gone,\r\nso y'can do what needs doin'."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "128||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-aniki. Be careful out there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "129||||4"
msgid "Who are you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "130||||4"
msgid "[Surround him! Don't let him escape!\r\nThis is where he dies!]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "131||||4"
msgid "The Chinese? I guess you've been\r\nwaiting for Akiyama to come back."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "132||||4"
msgid "Guess negotiations are off the table."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "133||||4"
msgid "[I'll slice you up!\r\nThe yakuza are done for!]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "134||||4"
msgid "[Dammit, who is this guy!?\r\nCome on, let's get out of here!]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "136||||4"
msgid "You're still here. Shouldn't you be\r\nrunning away with your friends?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||||4"
msgid "Hold on, Kiryu-san. It's me.\r\nYou remember?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "138||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "139||||4"
msgid "Oh, you're the guy who showed me\r\nthis place a while back."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140||||4"
msgid "Thank god you recognize me. I was worried\r\nyou were gonna start punching <font_kind=yakuza_italic>me</font_kind> soon."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||||4"
msgid "But Kiryu-san, what are you doing here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||||4"
msgid "Akiyama-san hasn't come back down to\r\nthese sewers since he left with you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||||4"
msgid "I need to get in touch with him again."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "144||||4"
msgid "Do you know how to reach him?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "145||||4"
msgid "I do, but it'll take a bit of time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "146||||4"
msgid "Akiyama-san's super careful."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "147||||4"
msgid "You've gotta go through a whole web of\r\npeople if you ever wanna contact him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "148||||4"
msgid "Right. After all, the triads\r\nstill have him in their crosshairs."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "149||||4"
msgid "Honestly, I think he should just get outta\r\nKamurocho entirely if it's that bad."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "150||||4"
msgid "Anyway, do you think you could\r\ntell Akiyama to give me a call?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "151||||4"
msgid "Can do. Just give me some time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "152||||4"
msgid "Okay. Thanks."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "153||||4"
msgid "(There's nothing for me to do now but walk\r\naround town and wait for Akiyama to call...)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "154||||4"
msgid "(Hm? They blocked the exit.\r\nI guess I have to go the other way...)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "155||||4"
msgid "This is Kiryu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "156||||4"
msgid "It's Akiyama. Sorry it's so tough to reach me.\r\nI heard you want something?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "157||||4"
msgid "I do. Where are you right now?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "158||||4"
msgid "Let's just say I'm on the move.\r\nStill in Kamurocho, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "159||||4"
msgid "Great. There's something I need to ask you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "160||||4"
msgid "The other day, we fought against that\r\ntriad guy, Ed, remember?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "161||||4"
msgid "How high up the ladder do you think he is?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "162||||4"
msgid "You mean in the Saio?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "163||||4"
msgid "I'm pretty certain he's an officer. He's one\r\nof the few who talks to their boss directly."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "164||||4"
msgid "I thought so.\r\nI want to speak to him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "165||||4"
msgid "Do you have any idea where he is?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "166||||4"
msgid "You wanna talk to Ed?\r\nBut why?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "167||||4"
msgid "The Saio Triad might've been involved\r\nin Haruka's accident in some way."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "168||||4"
msgid "Ed should be in Little Asia."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "169||||4"
msgid "He's the head honcho of that\r\nhuge building in the middle, but... Hm..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "170||||4"
msgid "What is it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "171||||4"
msgid "If you just stroll in asking to talk to Ed,\r\nyou'll have an ice cube's chance in hell."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "172||||4"
msgid "That place is the Saio Triad nerve center.\r\nMay as well walk up and declare war."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "173||||4"
msgid "If that's what it takes, so be it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "174||||4"
msgid "Not exactly what I wanna hear from\r\na guy who says he's gone clean."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "175||||4"
msgid "Anyway, it's clear we need to talk.\r\nAre you free now?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "176||||4"
msgid "Is that okay?\r\nWhere to?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "177||||4"
msgid "Over in Theater Square, there's an APA Hotel.\r\nMeet me up on the sixth floor."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "178||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san, you're alone, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "179||||4"
msgid "Yeah, I am."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "180||||4"
msgid "Great. I'll head over, then."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "181||||4"
msgid "Oh, and try to make sure you don't\r\nget followed this time, Kiryu-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "182||||4"
msgid "Heh. You got it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "183||||4"
msgid "(Time to go meet Akiyama.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "184||||4"
msgid "(This is the APA Hotel. Akiyama said\r\nhe'd be on the sixth floor.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "185||||4"
msgid "(It looks like I'm being followed, but they\r\nclearly won't start a fight out in public.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "186||||4"
msgid "(I need to take care of them before\r\nI can go up to meet Akiyama, though.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "187||||4"
msgid "(Maybe I should walk over to somewhere\r\nmore secluded so we can \"chat\" a bit.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "188||||4"
msgid "(Theater Alley would be the perfect place.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "189||||4"
msgid "So you're the ones who have\r\nbeen following me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "190||||4"
msgid "So much for talking."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "191||||4"
msgid "Wait, these are Tojo men?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "192||||4"
msgid "What's going on here?\r\nWhy is the Tojo Clan following me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "193||||4"
msgid "(I'm in the clear now.\r\nI should go meet up with Akiyama.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "194||||4"
msgid "(That door is open.\r\nAm I supposed to go in there?)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "195||||4"
msgid "Akiyama!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "196||||4"
msgid "Hey. Kinda like a spy, yeah?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "197||||4"
msgid "Sad part is that I'm not joking."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "198||||4"
msgid "You say that, but it looks like\r\nyou're enjoying yourself."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "199||||4"
msgid "On a more serious note, it's been a real\r\npain for me to get around Kamurocho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "200||||4"
msgid "Plus, today I thought I should play it\r\nextra safe. I have a guest with me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "201||||4"
msgid "A guest?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "202||||4"
msgid "I'm Murota from the Jinsei Family."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "203||||4"
msgid "I still haven't forgotten what you did\r\nfor me in that alleyway, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "204||||4"
msgid "Wait... Why are you here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "205||||4"
msgid "Well, Murota-kun and I started talking\r\nwhen he saw through my disguise."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "206||||4"
msgid "He mentioned how he led you to me when\r\nI was living in the sewer, and we hit it off."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "208||||4"
msgid "Apparently the triads aren't the only\r\nones we need to be worrying about."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "209||||4"
msgid "Sugai from the Tojo Clan\r\nis just as dangerous."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "210||||4"
msgid "But anyway, it might be best for you to hear\r\nall the details directly from Murota-kun."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "211||||4"
msgid "What can you tell me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "212||||4"
msgid "Man, you really are the fourth chairman!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "213||||4"
msgid "It was a huge shock when I realized\r\nwho you were after you saved me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "214||||4"
msgid "Anyway, the Tojo Clan execs are annoyed\r\nthat you're back. Almost more of a panic."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "215||||4"
msgid "Why?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "216||||4"
msgid "Well right now, control of the Tojo Clan rests\r\nwith Acting Chairman Sugai and Someya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "217||||4"
msgid "Of course, that's only because\r\nthe sixth chairman was arrested."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "218||||4"
msgid "Speaking of his arrest, I've heard rumors\r\nthat the whole thing was planned."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "219||||4"
msgid "What do you mean?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "220||||4"
msgid "Let me explain from the beginning.\r\nFirst we had that arson in Little Asia."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "221||||4"
msgid "Several fires flared up at the same time,\r\nyet they still couldn't make a single arrest."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "222||||4"
msgid "At that point, the only group who could carry\r\nout such a coordinated plan was the Tojo Clan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "223||||4"
msgid "You're telling me the Tojo Clan\r\nburned down Little Asia?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "224||||4"
msgid "Exactly. After the fire, Little Asia was ripe\r\nfor the Saio Triad to move into the ruins."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "225||||4"
msgid "That's when the turf war erupted."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "226||||4"
msgid "When that conflict escalated, the cops blamed\r\nthe Tojo Clan sixth chairman and arrested him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "227||||4"
msgid "The power vacuum that arrest created was\r\nsoon filled by a lifelong advisor, Sugai-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "228||||4"
msgid "Rumor has it,\r\nSugai was in bed with the Saio Triad."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "229||||4"
msgid "The point of the Little Asia fire was to\r\ncreate a space the Saio could move into."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "230||||4"
msgid "And the \"war\" he incited was all staged\r\nin order to bring down the sixth chairman."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "232||||4"
msgid "So imagine how Sugai must've felt when you\r\nshowed up just as he drove Daigo-san out."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "233||||4"
msgid "It's no surprise he wanted to keep\r\nhis distance from you, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "234||||4"
msgid "If you had realized what actually happened,\r\nyou might've come to avenge Daigo-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "235||||4"
msgid "I thought it'd be pretty important for\r\nyou to know about this, Fourth Chairman."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "236||||4"
msgid "Please try to be extra careful\r\naround Sugai and Someya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "237||||4"
msgid "Funny you say that. I got attacked\r\nby some Tojo guys on my way here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "238||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "239||||4"
msgid "It looks like these rumors of yours\r\naren't very far from the truth."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "241||||4"
msgid "I appreciate you telling me all this, Murota.\r\nI owe you one."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "242||||4"
msgid "Not at all.\r\nAnyway, I should be going."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "243||||4"
msgid "Murota's not the only one in the Tojo Clan\r\nwho thinks the rumors are true."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "244||||4"
msgid "But with Sugai and Someya watching their\r\nevery move, nobody can say anything."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "245||||4"
msgid "And what are your thoughts?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "246||||4"
msgid "About Sugai and the Saio conspiring?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "247||||4"
msgid "At a bare minimum, I know they\r\nreally want to kill each other now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "248||||4"
msgid "Even if the war started as some kind of act,\r\nit's blossomed into something very real now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "250||||4"
msgid "Kamurocho's such a goddamn mess."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "251||||4"
msgid "Even if I wanted to reopen Sky Finance,\r\nit'd be totally impossible in this climate."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "252||||4"
msgid "You'd reopen Sky Finance?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "253||||4"
msgid "Well, I only started it up to give loans\r\nto those who dreamed of saving this city."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "254||||4"
msgid "This place picked me back up when I was\r\nat rock bottom, so it's only fair I repay it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "255||||4"
msgid "But not only is it apparently open-season on\r\ncrime, but the Jingweon are on a spending spree."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "256||||4"
msgid "As you might have heard,\r\neven Stardust fell victim to that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "257||||4"
msgid "Yeah, I've heard."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "258||||4"
msgid "If there's any hope left in this town, it's\r\nbecause the Dragon of Dojima has returned."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "259||||4"
msgid "Yeah right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "260||||4"
msgid "I know, I know. Putting an end to this conflict\r\nis probably the last thing on your mind."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "261||||4"
msgid "But to be blunt with you,\r\nI kinda hope you'll do it anyway."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "263||||4"
msgid "Sorry. That was selfish of me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "264||||4"
msgid "I've looked into Little Asia."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "265||||4"
msgid "Kicking down the front door may not\r\nbe the only way to get to Ed."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "266||||4"
msgid "There's an alternate route."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "267||||4"
msgid "An alternate route?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "268||||4"
msgid "One that'll help us avoid\r\nthe Saio mob at the entrance."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "269||||4"
msgid "They'll never see us coming."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "270||||4"
msgid "By the way, what is it you're\r\nhoping to ask Ed?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "271||||4"
msgid "I want to know why the Saio Triad\r\nkilled a man named Tatsukawa."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "272||||4"
msgid "Tatsukawa?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "273||||4"
msgid "An ex-yakuza from Onomichi. More recently,\r\nhe was working as a Saio Triad informant."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "274||||4"
msgid "Beyond that, he's apparently Haruto's dad."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "275||||4"
msgid "Huh? You're saying Haruka-chan got with\r\na guy like that? No way."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "276||||4"
msgid "I have my doubts too. That's why I\r\nwant to have a talk with Ed."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "277||||4"
msgid "I get you. Okay then,\r\nI'll help you get into Little Asia."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "278||||4"
msgid "You sure?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "279||||4"
msgid "Yeah, I'll be fine. Let's meet up\r\nagain near the border of Little Asia."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "280||||4"
msgid "I'd feel better with more guys, though..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "281||||4"
msgid "Actually, I have two friends from Onomichi\r\nthat I can bring with me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "282||||4"
msgid "Perfect. Sorry I keep dragging you all\r\naround town. Anyway, I'll see you later."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "283||||4"
msgid "(I should head back to Serena and\r\nmeet up with Nagumo and Yuta.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "284||||4"
msgid "I'm back.\r\nWere you bored? Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "286||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-aniki. Sorry 'bout this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "287||||4"
msgid "Cap jus' wouldn't stop drinking.\r\nTurns out he still had a soft spot for Tatsukawa."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "288||||4"
msgid "I was kinda hoping t'drink myself, but he\r\ndowned it all before I got the chance."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "289||||4"
msgid "Yeah, well... I know you two are feeling low...\r\nBut that sake's worth 50 grand."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "290||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "291||||4"
msgid "One bottle is 50,000 yen."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "292||||4"
msgid "Wait, what?\r\nSo ten is... 500,000!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "293||||4"
msgid "I did tell him to take it easy, didn't I?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "294||||4"
msgid "Cap! Y'gotta get up! Hey!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "295||||4"
msgid "...The hell?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "296||||4"
msgid "Yuta, y'shit. Y'should've stopped me\r\nway quicker, y'damn moron."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "297||||4"
msgid "Tatsukawa ain't worth 500 grand."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "298||||4"
msgid "Mama said she put it on our tab, so we can\r\nfigure out how to handle this later."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "299||||4"
msgid "Fer now, we need to talk about Little Asia.\r\nRight, Kiryu-aniki?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "300||||4"
msgid "Right. Are you sober enough, Nagumo?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "301||||4"
msgid "'Course I am."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "302||||4"
msgid "I ain't one t'doze off while we're talkin'\r\n'bout bustin' into the enemy base."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "303||||4"
msgid "Speakin' of, one second yer pummelin'\r\na Korean host, the next yer onto the triads."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "304||||4"
msgid "I like your style, Aniki.\r\nY'keep givin' me reasons t'whoop on guys!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "305||||4"
msgid "Hold on a sec. This is the crew who\r\nmurdered Tatsukawa in cold blood, yeah?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "306||||4"
msgid "Even if we do sneak into their base,\r\nhow're we gonna get out alive?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "307||||4"
msgid "Y'goin' limp!? Think about what\r\nwe're doin' in Kamurocho t'begin with!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "308||||4"
msgid "Why'd we come if it ain't worth dyin', huh!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "309||||4"
msgid "No, don't get careless."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "310||||4"
msgid "Our lives <font_kind=yakuza_italic>are</font_kind> on the line here.\r\nThese guys won't think twice about murder."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "311||||4"
msgid "All the same, this is how we're\r\ngonna honor Tatsukawa's memory."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "312||||4"
msgid "Y'best be ready t'get down, Yuta!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "313||||4"
msgid "Damn straight.\r\nKiryu-aniki. Are you ready?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "314||||4"
msgid "Yeah, it's about time.\r\nLet's head to Little Asia."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "315||||4"
msgid "All right! I'd follow ya t'the depths\r\no' hell n' back, Kiryu-aniki!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "316||||4"
msgid "(Akiyama said to meet him outside of\r\nLittle Asia. We should get going...)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "317||||4"
msgid "Aniki, this here's Little Asia. We're s'posed\r\nt'be meetin' that Akiyama fella here, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "318||||4"
msgid "Yeah."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "319||||4"
msgid "I'm over here, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "320||||4"
msgid "Follow me, but don't get too close."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "321||||4"
msgid "Nagumo, Yuta. That's Akiyama."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "322||||4"
msgid "Gotcha."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "323||||4"
msgid "Okay."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "324||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san. Ed should be in there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "325||||4"
msgid "It won't be quite as direct, but my\r\nalternate route should get us in unseen."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "326||||4"
msgid "Got it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "327||||4"
msgid "Come on, this way."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "328||||4"
msgid "Hey, the name's Akiyama.\r\nThese your Hiroshima friends, Kiryu-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "329||||4"
msgid "Yeah. Hirose Family Captain Nagumo\r\nand one of his subordinates, Yuta."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "330||||4"
msgid "Haruto's father Tatsukawa used to\r\nbe part of the Hirose Family as well."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "331||||4"
msgid "I'm Nagumo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "332||||4"
msgid "And I'm Yuta Usami. Kiryu-aniki's told us\r\na lot about you, Akiyama-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "333||||4"
msgid "He said yer a lender 'round these parts?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "334||||4"
msgid "I was. I'm not much more than\r\na homeless bum nowadays."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "335||||4"
msgid "That aside, lemme explain how we reach Ed.\r\nThis building will be our entry point."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "336||||4"
msgid "From there we'll pass through a few others."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "337||||4"
msgid "That will lead us right to a window on\r\nthe third story where we slip right through."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "338||||4"
msgid "Assuming all goes well, we should be able\r\nto get inside without any triads noticing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "339||||4"
msgid "How d'we know that Ed guy's\r\neven there right now?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "340||||4"
msgid "He usually is."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "341||||4"
msgid "If he's not, we'll just hang out a while.\r\nHiding inside's the easy part."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "342||||4"
msgid "This is the perfect plan, if we can\r\nmanage t'pull it off."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "343||||4"
msgid "Agreed."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "344||||4"
msgid "Maybe there were some other options,\r\nbut I don't mind as long as I can talk to Ed."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "345||||4"
msgid "Should we get going, Akiyama?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "346||||4"
msgid "Yeah."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "347||||4"
msgid "Oh, I almost forgot.\r\nI should give you this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "348||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "349||||4"
msgid "The Tojo Clan's fourth chairman raiding the\r\nSaio Triad HQ would be a hell of a problem."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "350||||4"
msgid "Give me some peace of mind.\r\nPretty good, yeah?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "351||||4"
msgid "I didn't think I'd end up wearing\r\nanother one of these things."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "352||||4"
msgid "Our old man had it figured out, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "353||||4"
msgid "For now, Kiryu-san and I will\r\nhead up to the roof."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "354||||4"
msgid "Nagumo-san and Yuta-kun will wait\r\ndown here until we're up there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "355||||4"
msgid "We'd really stand out if\r\nall four of us went in together."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "356||||4"
msgid "Once we're on the roof, we'll lower a rope\r\ndown. You two can use that to climb up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "357||||4"
msgid "No prob!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "358||||4"
msgid "Understood."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "359||||4"
msgid "Well, let's do this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "360||||4"
msgid "Try to keep it down."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "361||||4"
msgid "[Have you checked the shipments?]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "362||||4"
msgid "[Yes. They're all looking good.]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "363||||4"
msgid "[Sounds like our work is done, then.\r\nNice job.]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "364||||4"
msgid "[Looking forward to some time off.]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "365||||4"
msgid "[That reminds me,\r\nthink you'll be free tonight?]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "366||||4"
msgid "[I don't have any plans, but I'm not\r\ninterested in another cabaret club.]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "367||||4"
msgid "[C'mon. It'll be fun, I promise.]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "368||||4"
msgid "[Fine, I'll go if you insist. Just don't\r\ngo missing again when it's time to pay.]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "369||||4"
msgid "[I told you, that was an accident.]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "370||||4"
msgid "[Accident, my ass. Whatever.]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "371||||4"
msgid "[It really was!]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "372||||4"
msgid "Hold on."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "373||||4"
msgid "We're in the clear."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "374||||4"
msgid "Huh? Who that!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "375||||4"
msgid "Am I imagining things?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "376||||4"
msgid "Why you here!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "377||||4"
msgid "Shoot, they already found us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "378||||4"
msgid "He's finished."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "379||||4"
msgid "This way."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "380||||4"
msgid "Come on. We need to hurry."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "381||||4"
msgid "Hold on, Kiryu-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "382||||4"
msgid "Just gimme a break already."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "383||||4"
msgid "What you doing here!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "384||||4"
msgid "Intruders!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "385||||4"
msgid "This is turning into a real problem."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "386||||4"
msgid "[Apparently there are intruders\r\nin here somewhere.]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "387||||4"
msgid "[They're probably trying to hide.]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "388||||4"
msgid "[Let's find them!]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "389||||4"
msgid "[Where are you hiding!?]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "390||||4"
msgid "[I know you're here somewhere!]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "391||||4"
msgid "[Dammit, where are you!?]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "392||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san! Don't let them find you!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "393||||4"
msgid "Hm!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "394||||4"
msgid "Figures!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "396||||4"
msgid "Damn, this is starting to suck."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "397||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san! Go for it, now!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "398||||4"
msgid "Get out the window!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "399||||4"
msgid "Hey, you!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "401||||4"
msgid "What this!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "402||||4"
msgid "What going on here!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "403||||4"
msgid "Man, thought this was going\r\nsouth for a second there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "404||||4"
msgid "All right, let's get the\r\nother two up here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "405||||4"
msgid "Here goes!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "406||||4"
msgid "Come on."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "407||||4"
msgid "That's everyone."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "408||||4"
msgid "Come on, it's just this way."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "409||||4"
msgid "It's awfully quiet."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "410||||4"
msgid "Huh? Nobody home?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "411||||4"
msgid "It's probably some kind of trap."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "412||||4"
msgid "I was kind of hoping you were wrong."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "413||||4"
msgid "Jus' makes it more interestin'!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "414||||4"
msgid "Oh hell yeah!\r\nYer up 'gainst me now, y'bastard!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "415||||4"
msgid "Yuta! Get that one!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "416||||4"
msgid "The rest of these chumps are ours!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "417||||4"
msgid "Ed's probably on the second floor."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "418||||4"
msgid "You should head down, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "419||||4"
msgid "What do you want?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "420||||4"
msgid "About a man named Tatsukawa.\r\nHe was working as a Saio informant."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "421||||4"
msgid "You guys killed him, didn't you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "422||||4"
msgid "\"Us\" is not quite right.\r\nIt is more accurate to say... I killed him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "423||||4"
msgid "Why did you do it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "424||||4"
msgid "That's what you came to discuss?\r\nWhy the sudden interest in him?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "425||||4"
msgid "I asked you first."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "426||||4"
msgid "You have no right to question me\r\nabout that rat Tatsukawa."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "427||||4"
msgid "He betrayed the Saio Triad."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "428||||4"
msgid "Tatsukawa knew that death is the\r\nprice you pay for such treachery."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "430||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san, are you familiar with\r\nthe term <font_kind=yakuza_italic>heihaizi</font_kind>?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "431||||4"
msgid "<font_kind=yakuza_italic>Heihaizi</font_kind>?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "432||||4"
msgid "It is used to refer to children born\r\nin China outside of the one-child policy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "433||||4"
msgid "These children live in the shadows.\r\nThey have no official records, no place in society."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "434||||4"
msgid "As such, they live in squalor,\r\nand the government turns a blind eye."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "435||||4"
msgid "Some estimates claim they number\r\nin the hundreds of millions."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "436||||4"
msgid "This Tatsukawa you want answers about\r\nwas one such <font_kind=yakuza_italic>heihaizi</font_kind>."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "437||||4"
msgid "So he was actually Chinese?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "438||||4"
msgid "The Saio smuggles countless <font_kind=yakuza_italic>heihaizi</font_kind> into\r\nJapan and gives them new lives here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "439||||4"
msgid "In hopes of someday repaying this generosity,\r\nTatsukawa joined the Yomei Alliance."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "440||||4"
msgid "But somewhere along the way, he forgot what\r\nhe owed and turned his back on us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "441||||4"
msgid "He knew the punishment\r\nhe would face in doing so."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "442||||4"
msgid "In other words, he deserved it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "443||||4"
msgid "How exactly did Tatsukawa betray you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "444||||4"
msgid "Good question, but I have no obligation\r\nto share that with you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "445||||4"
msgid "If you're so interested in knowing, you'll\r\nhave to ask Tatsukawa yourself in hell."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "447||||4"
msgid "I will gladly show you the way there,\r\nKazuma Kiryu!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "450||||4"
msgid "I'm not done yet!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "451||||4"
msgid "It's about time for another righteous whoopin'!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "452||||4"
msgid "Nagumo!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "453||||4"
msgid "Y'didn't forget us, did ya!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "454||||4"
msgid "We can help, Kiryu-aniki!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "455||||4"
msgid "I've been itching for a workout like this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "456||||4"
msgid "Don't let your guard down."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "457||||4"
msgid "Let's go!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "458||||4"
msgid "I don't understand.\r\nWhat are you doing here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "459||||4"
msgid "A Yomei Alliance officer is\r\ncooperating with the triads?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "461||||4"
msgid "I thought you guys were signing a pact\r\nwith the Tojo Clan in Hiroshima."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "462||||4"
msgid "Even then, the Tojo Clan is at war with the\r\ntriads. They should be your enemies."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "463||||4"
msgid "I don't care what happens to the Yomei now.\r\nThey'll be gone soon enough."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "464||||4"
msgid "What?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "465||||4"
msgid "Listen, Kiryu-san. My only allegiance lies to\r\nthe triads. I've been a Saio man all along."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "466||||4"
msgid "What the hell?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "467||||4"
msgid "If that's true, you're no different\r\nthan Tatsukawa."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "468||||4"
msgid "Tatsukawa?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "469||||4"
msgid "Tatsukawa was actually Chinese,\r\nborn a <font_kind=yakuza_italic>heihaizi</font_kind> on the mainland."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "470||||4"
msgid "He'd been pretending to be\r\nJapanese since he was a kid."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "471||||4"
msgid "Right. We have that much in common."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "472||||4"
msgid "However, I'd never betray the Saio Triad\r\nlike that traitor Tatsukawa."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "473||||4"
msgid "Just who the hell are you guys?\r\nWhat were you doing in Hiroshima!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "474||||4"
msgid "Are you really in a position to ask questions?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "475||||4"
msgid "If anything, I should be questioning you.\r\nWhy did you sneak into Little Asia like this?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "476||||4"
msgid "If you don't want me to kill every last one\r\nof you here, you'd better start talking."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "477||||4"
msgid "I wanted to know why\r\nyour organization killed Tatsukawa."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "478||||4"
msgid "Tatsukawa... What's he to you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "479||||4"
msgid "Before he came to Kamurocho, he had a son,\r\nHaruto, with a girl named Haruka Sawamura."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "480||||4"
msgid "Haruka is like a daughter to me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "481||||4"
msgid "You're Haruka Sawamura's guardian?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "482||||4"
msgid "I see now. That means the baby you were\r\ntoting around Onomichi was actually hers!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "484||||4"
msgid "Masuzoe! Pull the trigger already!\r\nStop wasting our time here!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "485||||4"
msgid "I suggest you calm down, Ed-san.\r\nThe boss is here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "486||||4"
msgid "What!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "487||||4"
msgid "Hard t'believe they actually\r\nlet us outta there alive."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "488||||4"
msgid "Seriously. Why d'ya reckon those\r\nChinese guys didn't jus' kill us there?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "489||||4"
msgid "No idea. You think that Masuzoe guy\r\nmight not be so bad after all?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "490||||4"
msgid "Nah, fat chance."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "491||||4"
msgid "He's a piece o' work. Y'ain't got no\r\nidea how much he's put me through."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "492||||4"
msgid "I never figured on him bein' Chinese, though.\r\nHe's one o' them <font_kind=yakuza_italic>heihaizi</font_kind>, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "493||||4"
msgid "First Tatsukawa, n' now Masuzoe.\r\nI jus' don't get it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "494||||4"
msgid "What does <font_kind=yakuza_italic>heihaizi</font_kind> mean anyway?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "495||||4"
msgid "It's what they call a child who was born\r\noutside of China's one-child policy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "496||||4"
msgid "At least, that's what Ed said."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "497||||4"
msgid "Oh, I've heard of that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "498||||4"
msgid "Under the one-child policy, parents face\r\nheavy fines if they have more than one kid."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "499||||4"
msgid "But out in the rural parts of China,\r\nthere aren't enough hands to tend the farms."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "500||||4"
msgid "Families'll have a second\r\nor even a third kid to help out."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "501||||4"
msgid "They never submit any documentation,\r\nthough. That's how they avoid the fine."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "502||||4"
msgid "But since the kids are unregistered, they\r\ncan't get education, welfare, or medicine."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "503||||4"
msgid "Yer pretty damn smart.\r\nNot so surprisin' fer a Tokyo guy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "504||||4"
msgid "It seems like the Saio have been smuggling\r\nthese <font_kind=yakuza_italic>heihaizi</font_kind> into Japan for a while now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "505||||4"
msgid "They probably forged all their registration,\r\neffectively making them Japanese citizens."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "506||||4"
msgid "I guess you could call it some kind\r\nof \"human laundering\" scheme."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "507||||4"
msgid "And down in Hiroshima,\r\nis this laundering thing common?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "508||||4"
msgid "Today's the first I've heard of it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "509||||4"
msgid "But at the very least, Tatsukawa and Masuzoe\r\nworked their way up the Yomei Alliance ranks."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "510||||4"
msgid "I wonder if they were sent t'spy\r\non us by the triads."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "511||||4"
msgid "Do the Saio Triad and the Yomei Alliance\r\nhave some kind of history together?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "512||||4"
msgid "If they do, I ain't ever heard o' it.\r\nBut we're the bottom rung o' the Yomei ladder."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "513||||4"
msgid "I thought we were coming here for Tatsukawa,\r\nbut we've ended up in something much bigger."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "514||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san. Are you really gonna go\r\nmeet up with Lo tomorrow?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "515||||4"
msgid "Yeah. I need answers about Tatsukawa."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "516||||4"
msgid "If we don't find out why the triads felt\r\nit necessary to kill him in cold blood..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "517||||4"
msgid "...We'll never know for sure if Haruka's\r\naccident was really just an accident."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "518||||4"
msgid "And if they truly did mean to attack Haruka,\r\nit's possible the same thing will happen again."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "519||||4"
msgid "You're right. I guess this is the only way."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "520||||4"
msgid "Y'sure yer gonna be okay on yer own, Aniki?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "521||||4"
msgid "They already had a chance to kill me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "522||||4"
msgid "If they didn't do it then, I don't expect\r\nthem to try again tomorrow."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "523||||4"
msgid "I'm not entirely sure what Lo's planning,\r\nbut I've got no reason to refuse him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "524||||4"
msgid "I jus' wish we could go with ya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "525||||4"
msgid "After Tatsukawa n' Masuzoe, who knows what\r\nelse the triads're plannin' fer Hiroshima."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "526||||4"
msgid "Oh, I almost forgot."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "527||||4"
msgid "Do you remember when Lo was\r\ntalking to Masuzoe in Chinese?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "528||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "529||||4"
msgid "Thanks to the lessons I got from Tatsukawa,\r\nI could more or less tell what he was saying."
msgstr ""

